<Content>colored my stay I have spent 5 nights in this hotel after looking for one that could define a perfect stay : price , quality, and location. Market had it all . I can say that the web site page reflects reality. Rooms are a combination of modern and antique. Nice, unique shower and a room with all needed basics. Allthough i would recommend a mirror in the room not only in the bathroom. And also a bigger cupboard for a longer holiday. We had a minor problem in the first night . We did not have hot water, they fixed the problem in the morning and when we got back it was ok. But the good note of the hotel made it so that we did not take it into consideration. It is also closed to the center where you can shop , eat and have a wonderfull time. It is a 15 -20 minutes walk or 2 metro stations . The subway is 5 minutes or less from the hotel. The breakfast was delicios for all types of tastes. All fresh and well done. Never dinned in the restaurant but in the evening it was so crowded that we thought the food was delicios. The neighborhood is a silent one with nice people. I recommend Market hotel for all kinds of people . 
